’Щ@f268b7979824fef2811c511a053b4d62f04ef8f290578a1edc326c001f95ab42ЪTitle: title: bits ror
Path: Flags
Content:
``--signed, -s``
: Always treat input number as a signed number.
``--number-bytes, -n {int}``
: The word size in number of bytes. Must be 
``1``
, 
``2``
, 
``4``
, or 
``8``
 (defaults to the smallest of those that fits the input number).
